high_descs: Hang a left at the stove and walk to the green table on the left.
Pick up the fork on the table in between the bottle and the pan near the back.
Turn around and walk to the sink ahead.
Put the fork in the sink, rinse it for a few seconds, and pick it back up.
Turn right and look up at the counter top.
Put the rinsed fork on the counter to the left of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed fork on a counter.

high_descs: Walk to the kitchen table in front of the plate.
Grab a fork from the table.
Walk to the kitchen sink behind you.
Put the fork in the sink, wash it, then grab it.
Turn around to the kitchen counter on the right of the sink.
Place the fork on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Wash a dirty fork to place on a counter.

high_descs: Look down and walk to the table to your right, to where a yellow plate sits.
Grab the fork on the table.
Turn around, walk straight to the sink and look down.
Place the fork inside the sink, wash it and remove it.
With the fork, turn to your right and look up.
Place the clean fork on the counter to your left.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean fork on the counter.
